title: Universe
synopsis: Under the night sky feebly illuminated by innumerable twinkling stars, a little girl wanders alone through a magic world between darkness and dawan, that is not today and not tomorrow, inhabited by 6 billion solitudes. What will she encounter in this solitary night journey?
staff: [['Sakamoto, Maaya', ['Theme Song Performance']], ['Yoshinari, You', ['Key Animation']], ['Gekidan Inu Curry', ['Special Effects', ' Character Design', ' Background Art']], ['Kotani, Kyouko', ['Key Animation']]]
